# Nanoleaf-Screen-Mirror-for-KDE

Real-time screen mirroring to Nanoleaf Aurora/Lines/Canvas LED controllers over USB HID. KDE Plasma 6 + Wayland, PyQt6 system tray, kwin-DBUS capture backend. Single-device (one USB strip), not a generic LED controller platform.

## Stack
- Python 3.11+, PyQt6, numpy, dbus-next, hidapi, dacite
- KDE Plasma 6 + Wayland (screenshot2 / kwin DBus)
- USB HID protocol for Nanoleaf LED controllers

## Key Conventions
- Type hints everywhere
- No comments in code unless absolutely necessary
- Format + lint with ruff before committing
- Test coverage > 70%
